001package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent;
002
003import io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium.smart.SmartWebDriver;
004import io.cyborgcode.roa.validator.core.AssertionResult;
005import java.util.List;
006import lombok.experimental.Delegate;
007
008/**
009 * A specialized UI service fluent class that extends {@link UiServiceFluent}
010 * and delegates its functionalities to an existing instance of {@code UIServiceFluent}.
011 *
012 * <p>The generic type {@code T} represents a concrete implementation of {@link UiServiceFluent},
013 * ensuring fluent interface compatibility and enabling seamless method chaining.
014 *
015 * @author Cyborg Code Syndicate üíçüë®üíª
016 */
017public class SuperUiServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends UiServiceFluent<T> {
018
019   /**
020    * A delegate reference to the original {@link UiServiceFluent} instance.
021    */
022   @Delegate
023   private final UiServiceFluent<T> original;
024
025   /**
026    * Constructs an instance of {@code SuperUiServiceFluent} by wrapping an existing {@link UiServiceFluent}.
027    *
028    * @param uiServiceFluent The original {@link UiServiceFluent} instance to delegate functionality to.
029    */
030   public SuperUiServiceFluent(UiServiceFluent<T> uiServiceFluent) {
031      super(uiServiceFluent.getDriver());
032      this.original = uiServiceFluent;
033   }
034
035   /**
036    * Retrieves the {@link SmartWebDriver} instance used by the underlying {@link UiServiceFluent}.
037    *
038    * @return The {@link SmartWebDriver} instance.
039    */
040   @Override
041   public SmartWebDriver getDriver() {
042      return original.getDriver();
043   }
044
045   /**
046    * Executes validation using a list of assertion results.
047    *
048    * @param assertionResults A list of {@link AssertionResult} objects representing validation outcomes.
049    */
050   @Override
051   public void validation(List<AssertionResult<Object>> assertionResults) {
052      original.validation(assertionResults);
053   }
054
055}
